title: That feel when you get your secondary that you're not good at
body:
But you're still the only one that doesn't feed. No joke, like 24-25 minute game. Mid died 11 times, Top died 11 times. ADC and support died 7 times each.

I died 4 times and each was trying to bail them out. Not much I can do as a jungler when every lane is losing.
